Author: tokyogucci
Text: You're allowed to be upset about them following sex workers on Twitter. I also tried to be the "cool girlfriend" who was okay with my SO following Belle Delphine type e-girls on Instagram but it made me so jealous and annoyed - what's the thought process behind actively following them, you know? Sorry to focus entirely on that part of your post but it annoys me seeing my friends put up with things they're uncomfortable with just so they don't rock the boat, because they don't think they'll ever find better than their current partner.
